display_long_description:
Unleash Your Inner Bird in Aerial Dogfights and Races.

Ever dreamed of soaring through the skies as a majestic bird, engaging in thrilling air-to-air challenges, or participating in high-speed tag races?

We’ve been developing a unique bird flapping and gliding mechanic that brings this experience to life in our upcoming multiplayer game, currently dubbed “Wingit”.

We’ve created a basic block-out map and implemented an infection game mode for testing purposes. However, we’re eager to explore more game modes and perfect the overall experience.

Depending on how you choose to fly, this game can be quite a lot of exercise :)

Watch the attached video for a glimpse into the heart-pounding action and join our Discord to see where we take it next -- https://discord.com/invite/YrZwpCANQN
